'''Donorcycle''' is a [[derogatory]] term for a [[motorcycle]] ridden by someone who is likely to die due to either recklessness or the inherent risk of riding a motorcycle. A combination of ([[Organ (anatomy)|organ]]) donor and motorcycle, it apparently originates from [[emergency room]] personnel who often see motorcycle accident victims. It alludes to the high percentage of donated organs that come from motorcyclists.
